tags: Doctor friendliness,Treatment satisfaction,
review:
I'm looking to get some implants and have consulted several dentists, which has only added to my confusion. But one thing that became clear was that I needed to remove any gum infection before proceeding. I found Dr. Venkatesh through an online search and went to him because he was able to see me very soon. 

I am very pleased with the gentle care that he gave me. I also am very impressed that he seems to be such a down to earth doctor,  Although I went to him for periodontal care, it's very likely that I'll go back to him for the implants.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review: I should thank Practo for showing such a nice gentleman. I have never witnessed such a patient friendly doctor with high expertise. his patience, care and affectionate way of handling patients , clarity everything shows his quality. a great doctor, humility personified indeed. another doctor who assisted him for removing the wisdom tooth Dr. Madhu also has the same virtues. I highly recommend this doctor for any sort of dental problems. thank you very much doctor for everything and also for making us to believe in the value based medical treatment.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review:
I visited the doctor for the filling replacement done in other clinic, since the filling done I was suffering too much severe headache and improper sleep. unable to do my daily work. 
I approached Dr. Katta's Clinic. The doctor took a x-ray and had a look at it  and as he advised there was no need for change of filling. But I again told that since the day of filling done, I am having health issues and I am not comfortable with the filling.   
            The doctor removed the old filling which was done
and  another filling was done. I am now fine and all my headache and other symptoms disappeared. I am feeling much better. 

Thank you doctor I am feeling much better now.
